    "Html": "\r\n<p>The problem is that the Graph representation is hidden because the Graph is built via</p>\r\n<p>&lt;zoom:ZoomControl &nbsp;Grid.Row=&quot;1&quot; &nbsp;Zoom=&quot;0.2&quot;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; ZoomBoxOpacity=&quot;0.5&quot;<span style=\"white-space:pre\">\r\n</span><span style=\"white-space:pre\"></span>Background=&quot;#ff656565&quot;&gt;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"white-space:pre\"></span>&lt;local:VisGraphLayout x:Name=&quot;graphLayout&quot; Margin=&quot;10&quot;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Graph=&quot;{Binding\r\n<span style=\"white-space:pre\"></span>Path=Graph}&quot;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; LayoutAlgorithmType=&quot;{Binding Path=LayoutAlgorithmType,\r\n<span style=\"white-space:pre\"></span>Mode=OneWay}&quot;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; OverlapRemovalAlgorithmType=&quot;FSA&quot;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style=\"white-space:pre\">\r\n</span><span style=\"white-space:pre\"></span>HighlightAlgorithmType=&quot;Simple&quot; /&gt;<br>\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;/zoom:ZoomControl&gt;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Is there a way to reach the Vertex object while accesing the onClick method?</p>\r\n",
    "PostedDate": "2012-11-19T13:29:05.223-08:00",
    "UserRole": null,
    "MarkedAsAnswerDate": null
  },
